description:
Can't fall asleep? Disturbing sounds?

Give yourself a healthy sleep, relax and fall asleep to soothing sleep melodies: rain, water, wind, sea surf and many others. Create your own combinations of the sounds of nature, the city for relaxation and quiet sleep.

According to studies, scientists have found that the sounds of nature positively affect the human psyche. Thanks to Sleeps, you can defeat insomnia, nighttime anxiety and tinnitus.

The Sleeps app will help you:
- Get rid of insomnia and sleep well;
- Block extraneous sounds and sleep better;
- Get rid of tinnitus;
- Concentrate;
- Meditate.

And it will also help your baby to calm down and fall asleep, the application has a special selection for the little ones.

Features:
- More than 120 sounds and melodies for relaxation, meditation, sleep.
- Sounds of nature (rain, thunder, water, wind, sea, night, etc.);
- Sounds of the city (road, car, railway station);
- Musical relaxation;
- Background playback of sounds;
- Setting the volume of each sound;
- Internet is required for the "Music" section;
- Sleep timer;
- Night theme;
- Relax and fall asleep.
